data.description: Range Priced!! Seller will entertain offers between $309,900 to $319,000. Escape to your private haven in this rural and tranquil 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home nestled on a sprawling 4.64-acre oasis. This charming property boasts laminate flooring in the kitchen, living areas, and bathrooms, offering both style and durability. The cozy carpeting in the bedrooms enhances comfort and warmth. The open kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with a kitchen island, ample cabinet space, and all appliances. With a split bedroom floorplan, privacy is ensured, making this home ideal for families or hosting guests. The spacious owner's suite includes a large bathroom and a walk-in closet, providing a comfortable retreat. A separate workshop with a mini-split system provides endless possibilities for creative pursuits and projects. Two additional separate storage offers ample space for your belongings. A private well and an upgraded 400-amp panel add convenience and reliability to your daily living. Safety and security are paramount, with the property gated and completely fenced around the perimeter, providing peace of mind and privacy. This property is an ideal spot for stargazers, offering magnificent views of the mountains and stunning sunrise/sunset views with stunning natural surroundings. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a slice of paradise where comfort, convenience, and natural beauty come together in perfect harmony.
